          p Take an SUV for its spacious interior, power, and versatility. Perfect for your next family vacation and off-road adventures.
          a.link.card__link(href="#" aria-label="Learn More.") Learn More
        article.card.card_darker-cyan
          img.m-b__img(src="images/icon-luxury.svg" alt="")
